            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>curry powder</strong> and<strong> ground turmeric</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Add your <strong>basmati rice</strong> and cook for 1 min further, stirring to coat the grains in all of the spices</p><p>Add 300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/969.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
