            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, pat your <strong>smoked basa fillet[s]</strong> dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once the egg[s]<strong> </strong>is done, drain and add to the <strong>ice water</strong> (this stops any further cooking)</p><p>Tip: No ice? Run under very cold running water for 3 min, then set aside in a bowl of cold water</p>",
      "order": 5,
