    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked,<strong> </strong>gently flake the <strong>smoked basa </strong>and<strong> </strong>fluff the<strong> basmati rice</strong> with a fork</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and stir through the<strong> chopped parsley</strong> – this is your<strong> classic kedgeree</strong></p>",
