    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>egg</strong> <strong>quarters </strong>over the <strong>classic kedgeree</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>roasted tomatoes</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
